---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Leter privacy policy." />
    <title>Privacy | leter.net</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-surface">
      <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-text">‚Üê Back to home</a>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-muted">
          <p>
            This policy explains how leter.net handles data under its strict invite-only operating
            model.
          </p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">1. Service model and data controllers</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              leter.net operations are managed by
              <a
                class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
                href="https://lewsion.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
              >
                Lewsion Ltd.
              </a>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Mail routing and current mailbox provisioning use
              <a
                class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
                href="https://forwardemail.net"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
              >
                Forward Email
              </a>. While this provider model is active, applicable Forward Email privacy and terms
              frameworks also apply.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">2. Data categories currently processed</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">The following categories may be processed for operations and security:</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
              <li>account/contact details collected during invite provisioning;</li>
              <li>access logs, authentication logs, and abuse-handling logs;</li>
              <li>operational metadata required for delivery, safety, and diagnostics;</li>
              <li>DMARC and TLS reporting data used for mail-security monitoring.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-2">
              At present, some provisioning information is recorded manually by authorized
              provisioners as part of invite-only onboarding.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">3. Retention and deletion</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Operational logs and metadata are retained for up to one (1) day for system security
              and technical reliability, unless temporary extension is required for active abuse or
              legal review.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Accounts inactive for six (6) consecutive months may be scheduled for deletion. Notice
              is provided before deletion where operationally possible.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">4. Legal requests and disclosures</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Lewsion Ltd. follows a data-minimization approach. If disclosure is required by valid
              legal process under applicable law, only data that exists and is legally required may
              be disclosed.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">5. Cookies and analytics</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              leter.net currently does not run analytics trackers and does not use marketing or
              profiling cookies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">6. Account and alias update requests</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              For alias changes, identity updates, or operational correction requests, contact:
              <span class="text-text">operator@leter.net</span>
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">7. Contact channels</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Privacy: <span class="text-text">privacy@lewsion.com</span>
              <br />
              Legal: <span class="text-text">legal@lewsion.com</span>
              <br />
              Abuse: <span class="text-text">abuse@lewsion.com</span>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
